SUMMARY:Interbay KinderCare Family Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Interbay KinderCare for delicious complimentary\nfood\, age-appropriate activities\, gifts\, games for the kids\,\nand opportunities to meet our amazing teachers\,\nstaff\, and new Center Director!
