SUMMARY:Ceramic Wall Pockets One-Night Class
DESCRIPTION:Create your own ceramic wall pockets—perfect for fresh stems\, dried flowers\, or holding small everyday items. You’ll shape and assemble your piece using simple handbuilding techniques\, add texture or clean lines\, and finish it with your choice of glaze. A relaxed\, beginner-friendly class with a project you can actually use. \nThis is an all-levels handbuilding class\, no experience needed. All materials included. We’ll email you when pieces are fired and ready for pickup\, 2-3 weeks after class. \nFeel free to bring a beverage (alcohol permitted) if you’d like! This class is appropriate for all skill levels. Pieces will be fired and ready for pickup in 2-3 weeks. \nMember discount 50%. Use code MEMBER50 for a single purchase or MEMBERBOGO to buy one get one free\, and bring  a friend!
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/ceramic-wall-pockets-one-night-class/
LOCATION:Gather Pottery\, 1465 Elliott Ave W\, Seattle\, 98119\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://discovermagnolia.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/wall-pockets.jpg
END:VEVENT
