SUMMARY:Meet Up Magnolia- virtual networking
DESCRIPTION:Our member businesses know the value of networking. Join us for our virtual networking event\, Meet Up Magnolia\, on the  2nd Thursday of every month. \nHow does this virtual networking work? You simply log on to the Zoom link and will be paired into one-on-one chats for 8 to 10 minutes each. We will repeat the process for approximately 3 or 4 rounds. You even have the option to follow up after the meeting and send a message to one or more of the people you meet to keep the dialogue going. \nSo many people to meet\, so many professional relationships to build. Join us HERE.
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/meet-up-magnolia-virtual-networking-2024-12-12/2026-03-12/
LOCATION:https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85388228818?pwd=amdmUEMvcVo2YjhETkxkbGJCa1Q4Zz09
CATEGORIES:Networking
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://discovermagnolia.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Meet-Up-Magnolia-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Magnolia Chamber of Commerce":MAILTO:info@discovermagnolia.org
