SUMMARY:March Magnolia After Hours at Seattle Makers
DESCRIPTION:Our March After Hours is shaping up to be one of the most unique experiences we’ve offered. Join us on March 24th from 6:00–8:30pm as Seattle Makers opens their 12\,000+ square feet of creative space exclusively for our Chamber community. \nYou’ll get a guided tour through their incredible maker environment\, explore the endless possibilities for hands‑on creation\, and watch live t‑shirt printing in action. Even better — you’ll walk away with a custom t‑shirt you made yourself\, a fun reminder of the night. \nAlong the way\, you’ll meet fellow Chamber members\, learn the story behind one of our most innovative member businesses\, enjoy a little pizza\, and experience the kind of creative energy that makes Seattle Makers such a standout in our community. \nThis special group experience is offered to members for just $40 per person — a significant Chamber‑only discount. \n👉 Reserve your spot and join us for creativity\, connection\, and community.
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/march-magnolia-after-hours-at-seattle-makers/
LOCATION:Seattle Makers\, 3012 16th Ave W\, Seattle\, WA\, 98119\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art,Craft,Food,Networking,Tour
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://discovermagnolia.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/After-Hours-Makers.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Magnolia Chamber of Commerce":MAILTO:info@discovermagnolia.org
END:VEVENT
