SUMMARY:Interbay Summer Camps- The Little Gym
DESCRIPTION:Interbay summer camps are 3 hours of Serious Fun for kiddos 3-10 years of age! Camp consists of 2 hours of gym time\, and 1 hour of snacks and craft time. Every week brings a new and exciting theme for your camper and we always have blocks\, books and coloring pages on standby for those campers that need a break. Camps are held Monday-Wednesday from 1-4pm. We offer special discounted pricing for members and camp pack purchases. Non member pricing is $75 for a single camp pass. More information on pack pricing can be found via our scannable QR code. Priority registration opens February 1st.
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/interbay-summer-camps-the-little-gym/2026-04-01/
LOCATION:The Little Gym- Interbay\, 2213 15th Ave W\, Seattle\, WA\, 98119\, United States
CATEGORIES:Craft,Fitness,Food,Kids
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://discovermagnolia.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IB-Camp-2025-Flyer-002-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
