SUMMARY:Vino in the Village- April 25th 2026
DESCRIPTION:Vino in the Village\nSaturday\, April 25\, 2026\n5:30 to 8:30 pm\nMagnolia Village \nVino in the Village features 18 wineries offering delicious wines for tasting and purchase. And if you purchase two or more bottles from any winery\, you get a $5 discount in addition to being tax-free! \nOnline Orders will end at Noon April 25th; Walk-up orders start at 5:30 pm at Modeles Home Furnishing. \nAdvance tickets are $40\, Walk up price is $50
