SUMMARY:Business & Breakfast
DESCRIPTION:Our Business & Breakfast series brings local professionals together for meaningful networking\, practical business education\, and great conversation. Each session features a guest speaker or facilitator offering tools you can use right away—whether you’re growing your business\, strengthening your team\, or expanding your local connections. Join us\, enjoy a chef-prepared breakfast\, and start your morning with inspiration and community.
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/business-breakfast-2/2026-10-20/
